<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 05 at 10:44AM EST  by NWS NorthernIndiana</headline>
<description>...Intense Snow Showers Developing...
Snow showers will increase in intensity and coverage through the
noon hour. Winds gusting to 40 mph will produce blowing snow and
low visibility in heavy snow showers.
North, south roadways including US 421, 35 and 31 will be impacted
in places with low visibilities and slick road conditions.</description>
